title: Handle for a squeegee or the like

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a handle for a squeegee or the like, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is an upper front left perspective view of a handle for a squeegee or the like showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is a right side elevational view thereof, the left side being a mirror image;
FIG. 3 is a front elevational view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a rear elevational view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a top plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 6 is a bottom plan view thereof.
The broken lines in FIGS. 1–6 showing a grip, fins, and/or a squeegee attached to the handle design are for illustrative purposes only and form no part of the claimed design.
